{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775863513745,"sessionID":"ses_28649817fffe9AkP3UViOSPpKA","part":{"id":"prt_d79b6be7f00194m4cLDZnd0XBp","messageID":"msg_d79b6b140001gZtQefQJ05m8Qu","sessionID":"ses_28649817fffe9AkP3UViOSPpKA","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_bbbcf5a68fd04748a07e4be0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: \"\"\"AgentCube provider for deploying AgentRuntime Custom Resources.\"\"\"\n2: \n3: from __future__ import annotations\n4: \n5: import os\n6: import re\n7: from typing import Any, Dict, Optional\n8: \n9: try:\n10:     from kubernetes import client, config\n11:     from kubernetes.client.rest import ApiException\n12: except ImportError:\n13:     client = None  # type: ignore[misc]\n14:     config = None  # type: ignore[misc]\n15:     ApiException = Exception  # type: ignore[misc, assignment]\n16: \n17: \n18: class AgentCubeProvider:\n19:     \"\"\"Provider for deploying agents as AgentRuntime Custom Resources.\"\"\"\n20: \n21:     CRD_GROUP = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n22:     CRD_VERSION = \"v1alpha1\"\n23:     CRD_PLURAL = \"agentruntimes\"\n24: \n25:     def __init__(self, namespace: str = \"default\", verbose: bool = False) -> None:\n26:         self.namespace = namespace\n27:         self.verbose = verbose\n28:         self._custom_api = client.CustomObjectsApi()\n29: \n30:     def _sanitize_name(self, name: str) -> str:\n31:         \"\"\"Sanitize a name for use as a Kubernetes resource name.\n32: \n33:         Replaces invalid characters with '-' and truncates to 63 characters.\n34:         \"\"\"\n35:         sanitized = re.sub(r\"[^a-z0-9\\-]\", \"-\", name.lower())\n36:         sanitized = sanitized.strip(\"-\")\n37:         if len(sanitized) > 63:\n38:             sanitized = sanitized[:63].rstrip(\"-\")\n39:         return sanitized\n40: \n41:     def deploy_agent_runtime(\n42:         self,\n43:         agent_name: str,\n44:         image_url: str,\n45:         port: int,\n46:         entrypoint: str,\n47:         env_vars: Dict[str, str],\n48:         workload_manager_url: str,\n49:         router_url: str,\n50:         readiness_probe_path: str,\n51:         readiness_probe_port: int,\n52:     ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n53:         \"\"\"Deploy an AgentRuntime Custom Resource to Kubernetes.\n54: \n55:         Args:\n56:             agent_name: Name of the agent.\n57:             image_url: Container image URL.\n58:             port: Port the agent listens on.\n59:             entrypoint: Command to start the agent.\n60:             env_vars: Environment variables for the container.\n61:             workload_manager_url: URL for the Workload Manager.\n62:             router_url: URL for the Router.\n63:             readiness_probe_path: Path for readiness probe.\n64:             readiness_probe_port: Port for readiness probe.\n65: \n66:         Returns:\n67:             Dict with 'name' and 'endpoint' keys.\n68:         \"\"\"\n69:         sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n70: \n71:         resolved_env = []\n72:         for key, value in env_vars.items():\n73:             resolved_env.append({\"name\": key, \"value\": value})\n74: \n75:         for key in [\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\", \"ROUTER_URL\"]:\n76:             env_value = os.environ.get(key)\n77:             if env_value and not any(e[\"name\"] == key for e in resolved_env):\n78:                 resolved_env.append({\"name\": key, \"value\": env_value})\n79: \n80:         cr_spec = {\n81:             \"apiVersion\": f\"{self.CRD_GROUP}/{self.CRD_VERSION}\",\n82:             \"kind\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n83:             \"metadata\": {\n84:                 \"name\": sanitized_name,\n85:                 \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n86:             },\n87:             \"spec\": {\n88:                 \"image\": image_url,\n89:                 \"port\": port,\n90:                 \"entrypoint\": entrypoint,\n91:                 \"env\": resolved_env,\n92:                 \"workloadManagerUrl\": workload_manager_url,\n93:                 \"routerUrl\": router_url,\n94:                 \"readinessProbe\": {\n95:                     \"path\": readiness_probe_path,\n96:                     \"port\": readiness_probe_port,\n97:                 },\n98:                 \"sessionTimeout\": \"15m\",\n99:                 \"maxSessionDuration\": \"8h\",\n100:                 \"imagePullSecrets\": [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}],\n101:             },\n102:         }\n103: \n104:         self._custom_api.create_namespaced_custom_object(\n105:             group=self.CRD_GROUP,\n106:             version=self.CRD_VERSION,\n107:             namespace=self.namespace,\n108:             plural=self.CRD_PLURAL,\n109:             body=cr_spec,\n110:         )\n111: \n112:         endpoint = f\"{router_url}/v1/agents/{sanitized_name}\"\n113:         return {\"name\": sanitized_name, \"endpoint\": endpoint}\n114: \n115:     def update_agent_runtime(\n116:         self,\n117:         name: str,\n118:         image_url: Optional[str] = None,\n119:         port: Optional[int] = None,\n120:         entrypoint: Optional[str] = None,\n121:         env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n122:         workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n123:         router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n124:         readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = None,\n125:         readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = None,\n126:     ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n127:         \"\"\"Patch an existing AgentRuntime Custom Resource.\n128: \n129:         If the CR does not exist (404), falls back to deploy_agent_runtime.\n130: \n131:         Args:\n132:             name: The CR name.\n133:             image_url: New container image URL.\n134:             port: New port the agent listens on.\n135:             entrypoint: New command to start the agent.\n136:             env_vars: New environment variables.\n137:             workload_manager_url: New Workload Manager URL.\n138:             router_url: New Router URL.\n139:             readiness_probe_path: New readiness probe path.\n140:             readiness_probe_port: New readiness probe port.\n141: \n142:         Returns:\n143:             Dict with 'name' and 'endpoint' keys.\n144:         \"\"\"\n145:         sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(name)\n146: \n147:         spec_patch: Dict[str, Any] = {}\n148:         if image_url is not None:\n149:             spec_patch[\"image\"] = image_url\n150:         if port is not None:\n151:             spec_patch[\"port\"] = port\n152:         if entrypoint is not None:\n153:             spec_patch[\"entrypoint\"] = entrypoint\n154:         if env_vars is not None:\n155:             resolved_env = []\n156:             for key, value in env_vars.items():\n157:                 resolved_env.append({\"name\": key, \"value\": value})\n158:             spec_patch[\"env\"] = resolved_env\n159:         if workload_manager_url is not None:\n160:             spec_patch[\"workloadManagerUrl\"] = workload_manager_url\n161:         if router_url is not None:\n162:             spec_patch[\"routerUrl\"] = router_url\n163:         if readiness_probe_path is not None or readiness_probe_port is not None:\n164:             probe: Dict[str, Any] = {}\n165:             if readiness_probe_path is not None:\n166:                 probe[\"path\"] = readiness_probe_path\n167:             if readiness_probe_port is not None:\n168:                 probe[\"port\"] = readiness_probe_port\n169:             spec_patch[\"readinessProbe\"] = probe\n170: \n171:         body = {\"spec\": spec_patch}\n172: \n173:         try:\n174:             self._custom_api.patch_namespaced_custom_object(\n175:                 group=self.CRD_GROUP,\n176:                 version=self.CRD_VERSION,\n177:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n178:                 plural=self.CRD_PLURAL,\n179:                 name=sanitized_name,\n180:                 body=body,\n181:             )\n182:         except ApiException as e:\n183:             if e.status == 404:\n184:                 return self.deploy_agent_runtime(\n185:                     agent_name=name,\n186:                     image_url=image_url or \"\",\n187:                     port=port or 8080,\n188:                     entrypoint=entrypoint or \"\",\n189:                     env_vars=env_vars or {},\n190:                     workload_manager_url=workload_manager_url or \"\",\n191:                     router_url=router_url or \"\",\n192:                     readiness_probe_path=readiness_probe_path or \"/health\",\n193:                     readiness_probe_port=readiness_probe_port or 8080,\n194:                 )\n195:             raise\n196: \n197:         endpoint = f\"{router_url or ''}/v1/agents/{sanitized_name}\"\n198:         return {\"name\": sanitized_name, \"endpoint\": endpoint}\n199: \n200:     def delete_agent_runtime(self, name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n201:         \"\"\"Delete an AgentRuntime Custom Resource.\n202: \n203:         Args:\n204:             name: The CR name.\n205: \n206:         Returns:\n207:             Dict with status, name, namespace.\n208:         \"\"\"\n209:         sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(name)\n210:         try:\n211:             self._custom_api.delete_namespaced_custom_object(\n212:                 group=self.CRD_GROUP,\n213:                 version=self.CRD_VERSION,\n214:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n215:                 plural=self.CRD_PLURAL,\n216:                 name=sanitized_name,\n217:             )\n218:         except ApiException as e:\n219:             if e.status == 404:\n220:                 return {\n221:                     \"status\": \"deleted\",\n222:                     \"name\": sanitized_name,\n223:                     \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n224:                 }\n225:             raise\n226: \n227:         return {\n228:             \"status\": \"deleted\",\n229:             \"name\": sanitized_name,\n230:             \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n231:         }\n232: \n233:     def get_agent_runtime(self, name: str) -> Optional[Dict[str, Any]]:\n234:         \"\"\"Retrieve an existing AgentRuntime CR by name.\n235: \n236:         Args:\n237:             name: The CR name.\n238: \n239:         Returns:\n240:             The CR dict if found, None otherwise.\n241:         \"\"\"\n242:         try:\n243:             return self._custom_api.get_namespaced_custom_object(\n244:                 group=self.CRD_GROUP,\n245:                 version=self.CRD_VERSION,\n246:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n247:                 plural=self.CRD_PLURAL,\n248:                 name=name,\n249:             )\n250:         except ApiException as e:\n251:             if e.status == 404:\n252:                 return None\n253:             raise\n\n(End of file - total 253 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"\"\"\"AgentCube provider for deploying AgentRuntime Custom Resources.\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport os\nimport re\nfrom typing import Any, Dict, Optional\n\ntry:\n    from kubernetes import client, config\n    from kubernetes.client.rest import ApiException\nexcept ImportError:\n    client = None  # type: ignore[misc]\n    config = None  # type: ignore[misc]\n    ApiException = Exception  # type: ignore[misc, assignment]\n\n\nclass AgentCubeProvider:\n    \"\"\"Provider for deploying agents as AgentRuntime Custom Resources.\"\"\"\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py","time":{"start":1775863513730,"end":1775863513742}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775863515047,"sessionID":"ses_28649817fffe9AkP3UViOSPpKA","part":{"id":"prt_d79b6c310001yRYSRrjfWjeSdh","messageID":"msg_d79b6b140001gZtQefQJ05m8Qu","sessionID":"ses_28649817fffe9AkP3UViOSPpKA","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_7462a44e0b494ffbbb4d8781","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/services/test_agentcube_provider.py"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/services/test_agentcube_provider.py</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: \"\"\"Tests for AgentCubeProvider.\"\"\"\n2: \n3: from unittest.mock import MagicMock, patch\n4: \n5: import pytest\n6: \n7: from agentcube.services.agentcube_provider import AgentCubeProvider\n8: \n9: \n10: class TestAgentCubeProvider_DeployCR:\n11:     def test_creates_agent_runtime_cr_with_correct_spec(self) -> None:\n12:         mock_api = MagicMock()\n13:         with patch(\"agentcube.services.agentcube_provider.client.CustomObjectsApi\", return_value=mock_api):\n14:             provider = AgentCubeProvider(namespace=\"default\")\n15:             result = provider.deploy_agent_runtime(\n16:                 agent_name=\"test-agent\",\n17:                 image_url=\"registry.example.com/test-agent:v1.0.0\",\n18:                 port=8080,\n19:                 entrypoint=\"python main.py\",\n20:                 env_vars={\"KEY\": \"value\"},\n21:                 workload_manager_url=\"http://wm.example.com\",\n22:                 router_url=\"http://router.example.com\",\n23:                 readiness_probe_path=\"/health\",\n24:                 readiness_probe_port=8080,\n25:             )\n26: \n27:         assert result[\"name\"] == \"test-agent\"\n28:         assert result[\"endpoint\"] == \"http://router.example.com/v1/agents/test-agent\"\n29:         mock_api.create_namespaced_custom_object.assert_called_once()\n30:         call_kwargs = mock_api.create_namespaced_custom_object.call_args[1]\n31:         body = call_kwargs[\"body\"]\n32:         assert body[\"spec\"][\"image\"] == \"registry.example.com/test-agent:v1.0.0\"\n33:         assert body[\"spec\"][\"port\"] == 8080\n34:         assert body[\"spec\"][\"entrypoint\"] == \"python main.py\"\n35: \n36: \n37: class TestAgentCubeProvider_EnvVarFallback:\n38:     def test_falls_back_to_os_environ_for_missing_env_vars(self) -> None:\n39:         mock_api = MagicMock()\n40:         with patch(\"agentcube.services.agentcube_provider.client.CustomObjectsApi\", return_value=mock_api):\n41:             with patch(\"agentcube.services.agentcube_provider.os.environ.get\", side_effect=lambda k: \"env-value\" if k == \"ROUTER_URL\" else None):\n42:                 provider = AgentCubeProvider(namespace=\"default\")\n43:                 provider.deploy_agent_runtime(\n44:                     agent_name=\"test-agent\",\n45:                     image_url=\"registry.example.com/test-agent:v1.0.0\",\n46:                     port=8080,\n47:                     entrypoint=\"python main.py\",\n48:                     env_vars={},\n49:                     workload_manager_url=\"http://wm.example.com\",\n50:                     router_url=\"http://router.example.com\",\n51:                     readiness_probe_path=\"/health\",\n52:                     readiness_probe_port=8080,\n53:                 )\n54: \n55:         call_kwargs = mock_api.create_namespaced_custom_object.call_args[1]\n56:         body = call_kwargs[\"body\"]\n57:         env_list = body[\"spec\"][\"env\"]\n58:         router_env = [e for e in env_list if e[\"name\"] == \"ROUTER_URL\"]\n59:         assert len(router_env) == 1\n60:         assert router_env[0][\"value\"] == \"env-value\"\n61: \n62: \n63: class TestAgentCubeProvider_SessionConfig:\n64:     def test_cr_contains_session_timeout_and_max_duration(self) -> None:\n65:         mock_api = MagicMock()\n66:         with patch(\"agentcube.services.agentcube_provider.client.CustomObjectsApi\", return_value=mock_api):\n67:             provider = AgentCubeProvider(namespace=\"default\")\n68:             provider.deploy_agent_runtime(\n69:                 agent_name=\"test-agent\",\n70:                 image_url=\"registry.example.com/test-agent:v1.0.0\",\n71:                 port=8080,\n72:                 entrypoint=\"python main.py\",\n73:                 env_vars={},\n74:                 workload_manager_url=\"http://wm.example.com\",\n75:                 router_url=\"http://router.example.com\",\n76:                 readiness_probe_path=\"/health\",\n77:                 readiness_probe_port=8080,\n78:             )\n79: \n80:         call_kwargs = mock_api.create_namespaced_custom_object.call_args[1]\n81:         body = call_kwargs[\"body\"]\n82:         assert body[\"spec\"][\"sessionTimeout\"] == \"15m\"\n83:         assert body[\"spec\"][\"maxSessionDuration\"] == \"8h\"\n84: \n85: \n86: class TestAgentCubeProvider_ImagePullSecrets:\n87:     def test_cr_contains_image_pull_secrets(self) -> None:\n88:         mock_api = MagicMock()\n89:         with patch(\"agentcube.services.agentcube_provider.client.CustomObjectsApi\", return_value=mock_api):\n90:             provider = AgentCubeProvider(namespace=\"default\")\n91:             provider.deploy_agent_runtime(\n92:                 agent_name=\"test-agent\",\n93:                 image_url=\"registry.example.com/test-agent:v1.0.0\",\n94:                 port=8080,\n95:                 entrypoint=\"python main.py\",\n96:                 env_vars={},\n97:                 workload_manager_url=\"http://wm.example.com\",\n98:                 router_url=\"http://router.example.com\",\n99:                 readiness_probe_path=\"/health\",\n100:                 readiness_probe_port=8080,\n101:             )\n102: \n103:         call_kwargs = mock_api.create_namespaced_custom_object.call_args[1]\n104:         body = call_kwargs[\"body\"]\n105:         assert body[\"spec\"][\"imagePullSecrets\"] == [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}]\n106: \n107: \n108: class TestAgentCubeProvider_SanitizeName:\n109:     def test_invalid_chars_replaced(self) -> None:\n110:         provider = AgentCubeProvider()\n111:         assert provider._sanitize_name(\"my_agent.name\") == \"my-agent-name\"\n112: \n113:     def test_truncated_to_63_chars(self) -> None:\n114:         provider = AgentCubeProvider()\n115:         long_name = \"a\" * 70\n116:         result = provider._sanitize_name(long_name)\n117:         assert len(result) == 63\n118: \n119:     def test_uppercase_converted_to_lowercase(self) -> None:\n120:         provider = AgentCubeProvider()\n121:         assert provider._sanitize_name(\"MyAgent\") == \"myagent\"\n122: \n123:     def test_leading_trailing_dashes_stripped(self) -> None:\n124:         provider = AgentCubeProvider()\n125:         assert provider._sanitize_name(\"--my-agent--\") == \"my-agent\"\n126: \n127:     def test_empty_after_sanitization(self) -> None:\n128:         provider = AgentCubeProvider()\n129:         result = provider._sanitize_name(\"___\")\n130:         assert result == \"\"\n131: \n132: \n133: class TestAgentCubeProvider_GetAgentRuntime:\n134:     def test_returns_cr_when_exists(self) -> None:\n135:         mock_api = MagicMock()\n136:         mock_api.get_namespaced_custom_object.return_value = {\"metadata\": {\"name\": \"test-agent\"}}\n137:         with patch(\"agentcube.services.agentcube_provider.client.CustomObjectsApi\", return_value=mock_api):\n138:             provider = AgentCubeProvider(namespace=\"default\")\n139:             result = provider.get_agent_runtime(\"test-agent\")\n140:         assert result is not None\n141:         assert result[\"metadata\"][\"name\"] == \"test-agent\"\n142: \n143:     def test_returns_none_when_not_found(self) -> None:\n144:         from kubernetes.client.rest import ApiException\n145: \n146:         mock_api = MagicMock()\n147:         mock_api.get_namespaced_custom_object.side_effect = ApiException(status=404)\n148:         with patch(\"agentcube.services.agentcube_provider.client.CustomObjectsApi\", return_value=mock_api):\n149:             provider = AgentCubeProvider(namespace=\"default\")\n150:             result = provider.get_agent_runtime(\"nonexistent\")\n151:         assert result is None\n\n(End of file - total 151 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"\"\"\"Tests for AgentCubeProvider.\"\"\"\n\nfrom unittest.mock import MagicMock, patch\n\nimport pytest\n\nfrom agentcube.services.agentcube_provider import AgentCubeProvider\n\n\nclass TestAgentCubeProvider_DeployCR:\n    def test_creates_agent_runtime_cr_with_correct_spec(self) -> None:\n        mock_api = MagicMock()\n        with patch(\"agentcube.services.agentcube_provider.client.CustomObjectsApi\", return_value=mock_api):\n            provider = AgentCubeProvider(namespace=\"default\")\n            result = provider.deploy_agent_runtime(\n                agent_name=\"test-agent\",\n                image_url=\"registry.example.com/test-agent:v1.0.0\",\n                port=8080,\n                entrypoint=\"python main.py\",\n                env_vars={\"KEY\": \"value\"},","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/services/test_agentcube_provider.py","time":{"start":1775863515024,"end":1775863515044}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775863516333,"sessionID":"ses_28649817fffe9AkP3UViOSPpKA","part":{"id":"prt_d79b6c823001iHUCUg4jqDV065","messageID":"msg_d79b6b140001gZtQefQJ05m8Qu","sessionID":"ses_28649817fffe9AkP3UViOSPpKA","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_6634bf9b911a4ef5b076c598","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube 核心模块测试契约 (TDD Manifest)\n2: \n3: 本规范定义了系统各核心组件必须实现的最小测试集。未通过以下测试用例的实现将被判定为“跑偏”。\n4: \n5: ## 1. Workload Manager (Go) - 核心准入测试\n6: - **Func: `CreateSandbox`**\n7:     - **Test-WM-1**: 必须 Mock Kubernetes Client，验证 `sandbox` 资源被正确创建。\n8:     - **Test-WM-2**: 验证 Session 冲突处理（同名 Sandbox 冲突时返回 409 或恢复现有会话）。\n9:     - **Test-WM-3**: 验证 Pod 状态同步逻辑。模拟 Pod 变为 `Running` 状态，验证 API 返回正确的 `Endpoint`。\n10: - **Func: `DeleteSession`**\n11:     - **Test-WM-4**: 验证物理资源的清理。确保调用了 K8s Delete API 且 Redis 记录同步删除。\n12: \n13: ## 2. Router (Go) - 高并发与安全测试\n14: - **Middleware: `AuthMiddleware`**\n15:     - **Test-RT-1**: 构造非法 JWT，验证返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n16:     - **Test-RT-2**: 构造过期 JWT，验证返回 `Token Expired`。\n17: - **Proxy Logic: `HandleProxy`**\n18:     - **Test-RT-3**: 模拟后端超时，验证 Proxy 正确处理 `Gateway Timeout` 且不崩溃。\n19:     - **Test-RT-4**: 验证 Header 透传（Host, X-Forwarded-For 等）。\n20: \n21: ## 3. Session Store (Go) - 强一致性测试\n22: - **Store Interface: `RedisStore` / `ValkeyStore`**\n23:     - **Test-ST-1**: 验证对象序列化与反序列化（SessionInfo -> JSON -> SessionInfo）。\n24:     - **Test-ST-2**: 并发写测试。模拟 100 个并发请求写入同一 Session，验证无 Data Race。\n25: \n26: ## 4. PicoD (Go) - 执行引擎隔离测试\n27: - **Executor: `RunCode`**\n28:     - **Test-PD-1**: 验证资源限制（如 OOM）。模拟大内存分配，验证进程被正确杀掉并返回错误。\n29:     - **Test-PD-2**: 验证 Stdout 分块读取。处理超过 1MB 的输出，验证无缓冲区溢出。\n30: \n31: ## 5. Python SDK & CLI - 兼容性与易用性测试\n32: - **Class: `CodeInterpreterClient`**\n33:     - **Test-SDK-1**: 验证所有 HTTP 状态码映射。404 -> `NotFoundError`, 429 -> `RateLimitError`。\n34:     - **Test-SDK-2**: 验证文件上传协议。构造二进制流，验证 Multipart 封装符合 Router 规范。\n35: - **CLI: `kubectl-agentcube`**\n36:     - **Test-CLI-1**: 验证 `run` 命令的参数解析。测试 `--image`, `--env` 等参数的正确合并。\n37: \n38: ## 物理指标要求\n39: 1.  **测试/代码行数比 (T/C Ratio)**: 必须 > 0.4 (即每 100 行代码至少 40 行测试)。\n40: 2.  **用例完整性**: 每个源文件（`*.go`, `*.py`）必须存在对应的 `*_test.go` 或 `test_*.py`。\n\n(End of file - total 40 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube 核心模块测试契约 (TDD Manifest)\n\n本规范定义了系统各核心组件必须实现的最小测试集。未通过以下测试用例的实现将被判定为“跑偏”。\n\n## 1. Workload Manager (Go) - 核心准入测试\n- **Func: `CreateSandbox`**\n    - **Test-WM-1**: 必须 Mock Kubernetes Client，验证 `sandbox` 资源被正确创建。\n    - **Test-WM-2**: 验证 Session 冲突处理（同名 Sandbox 冲突时返回 409 或恢复现有会话）。\n    - **Test-WM-3**: 验证 Pod 状态同步逻辑。模拟 Pod 变为 `Running` 状态，验证 API 返回正确的 `Endpoint`。\n- **Func: `DeleteSession`**\n    - **Test-WM-4**: 验证物理资源的清理。确保调用了 K8s Delete API 且 Redis 记录同步删除。\n\n## 2. Router (Go) - 高并发与安全测试\n- **Middleware: `AuthMiddleware`**\n    - **Test-RT-1**: 构造非法 JWT，验证返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n    - **Test-RT-2**: 构造过期 JWT，验证返回 `Token Expired`。\n- **Proxy Logic: `HandleProxy`**\n    - **Test-RT-3**: 模拟后端超时，验证 Proxy 正确处理 `Gateway Timeout` 且不崩溃。\n    - **Test-RT-4**: 验证 Header 透传（Host, X-Forwarded-For 等）。\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md","time":{"start":1775863516325,"end":1775863516331}}}}
